{"tid":1447752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:10:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:16:23.000Z","uid":33373,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2432913d92e825ddd5c0a9ab747c6e3505acd247","tid":1447752,"uid":33373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:10:48.000Z","msg":"一人一 狂洗連登post [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=6RyWY35l7oH3ui7gcEo%2FTPMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=c2e71777\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=6RyWY35l7oH3ui7gcEo%2FTPMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=19dcfa3a\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"1e6d8e8fe1621d35ff0ac32309558be8ee1438dd","tid":1447752,"uid":79039,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:12:10.000Z","msg":"定係和理包圍各區狗屋或者狗總好？"},{"pid":"891f503bf1acfd4e5e1d63801a765439b714759c","tid":1447752,"uid":144084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:12:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/0/viewer?mid=1xkjAGpVuJRzy710odRB-xYY63jbwbf1_&amp;ll=22.375815103418088%2C114.146526&amp;z=11\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fd%2Fu%2F0%2Fviewer%3Fmid%3D1xkjAGpVuJRzy710odRB-xYY63jbwbf1_%26ll%3D22.375815103418088%252C114.146526%26z%3D11&d=6RyWY35l7oH3ui7gcEo%2FTPMFbVP